snippet.title: Outcast - A New Beginning | Legend of the Ulukaï (Part 1)
snippet.description:
Pre-Order Outcast - A New Beginning now!

Experience intense third person combat when Outcast - A New Beginning releases on March 15, 2024 on PC, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X|S. 

They called him renegade, traitor, an outcast on two planets. Listen to Maar telling you the Legend of the Ulukaï for Outcast - A New Beginning.
